name: The Backrooms 1998 - Found Footage Backroom Survival Horror Game

meta.shortDescription: The Backrooms: 1998 is a first-person found footage psychological horror survival game where it tells the story of a young teen after accidentally falling into the depths of The Backrooms in 1998. Roam freely, mark, explore and try unravel the story - however you are not alone. Don't scream.
